<br>
on my previous post on fun with multi mage groups,, I thought i would add some info for you all here about skyfire..<br>
<br>
now we all prob. know about the front zone, and even the overthere zone.. and perhaps even the far ne corner behind the statue where it's good for fearn' the mobs..<br>
<br>
what you all might not know is...<br>
<br>
if you head straight out *about* from bw, toward the veshan pk. zone, you will pass by a little island surrounded by lava, with a large skeleton of a dragon on it..<br>
<br>
now..  this is a place NO mob wanders to, and it is in the heart of good high level pulls.  good room to have a multi mage group.<br>
<br>
use air pets,, with malosi,,  weekest pet gets sent in last.  and by all  HAVE FUN!<br>
