<br>
If you fear kite, this is the place to be, as we refer to it as fear highway. The mobs take 3 steps out, turn left, then do a 180 and walks down the path that no mobs goto. Perfect for fear kitting. (Be sure they are snared 1st of course <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
If with all Magician's no fear required, just pull, shock 2 or 3 times and med as the pets rip it apart.<br>
<br>
I prefer this spot as it is away from Talendor, and the mobs are 95% blue to me at 60 and the other 5% light blue. So perfect, and pulling is easy, just avoide the guardian wurms. They quad 530's and will summon you.<br>
<br>
